item.title: My first blog
item.description: The Power of the music Music is present at every moment of our lives, whether it’s at home, in the car, thanks to a digital music player or during a concert. This art can be found in every culture too, considered as the common passion of the humanity. You don’t need to be a musician to like music, almost everybody like it. Some melodies make us feeling deep emotions or influence them and it turns out sometimes to be essential for our well-being and is used in some therapy.
